metadata.name: 3D Glasses
metadata.description:
This Bill Murray 1000 3D Glasses NFT can be redeemed for a soon-to-be-announced Bill Murray 1000 membership NFT, or a custom glasses attribute upgrade to your BM1000 OB or Destinations NFT.

To redeem your 3D Glasses NFT:
• Go to billmurray1000.com
• Click on the Membership link at the top of the page
• Connect your wallet
• Follow the instructions

For more information about the Bill Murray 1000 NFTs, join the Discord at: discord.com/invite/HnXFs2Deqv
